txt.en: Despite the Yule season, brave adventurers are still needed to complete missions across Middle-earth.
'We love that you've come to visit Frostbluff, but there's more to Yule than this lovely little town. Why don't you bring some Yule cheer to folks in need of aid across Middle-earth?'
A Mission to Bring Good Cheer
'Spread some Yule cheer, have you? Well done, friend.'
Missions can be completed across Middle-earth.\n\nYou should complete any mission.
Mara Sandydowns can be found near the entrance to Winter-home.\n\nYou have completed a mission during the Yule Festival. You should talk to Mara Sandydowns.
